metadata.name: RAY OF WONDER
metadata.description:
There is nothing like a stingray dancing through the ocean sunbeams.

Taken off the magical island of The Seychelles, this beauty captured my attention through the lens of my drone.

If you know me, I am obsessed with wildlife living in the ocean.

This image is where my passion for the ocean and it’s creatures all begun.

The moment I laid my eyes on this electric stingray, I felt an overwhelming feeling of love and understanding. 

I had to learn from the movement of the waves and focused on getting the perfect piece to make sure I captured this “Ray Of Wonder” in it’s purest form.

I hope this special piece finds a home to someone who loves the ocean and it’s life just as much as I do.

The winning bid will receive a 18"x24" inch fine art print.
